        "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You can Cast Spells using Mysticism.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Spells:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You learn 4 Spells, one of which must always be Polymorph. You learn 1 other Spell every 2 Levels in this Class hereafter.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Mana:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Your Maximum Mana is equal to (4 × your Druid Level), and the highest amount of Mana you can spend to Cast a Spell is equal to (Awareness + half your Druid Level, round up). You regain spent Mana when you Rest.</span></p>",
